title: New: dd ellle – Tell Me
body:
A few months since we heard any original material from the elusive **dd elle**, and he/she has returned with _Tell Me_, via Ryan Hemsworth’s now legendary Secret Songs.

The most openly vocal we’ve heard dd elle so far, it’s another bubblegum take on Jai Paul / Ben Khan’s Prince indebted sound, whilst remaining as effortlessly cool. Check out Tell Me below.
